Item Description:
Duda offers a visual design tool for agencies building websites.

  • Partner Portal
  • Hosting
  • Easy to use visual editor
  • CMS Editor for clients
  • Web Forms (drag and drop interface)
  • Blog
  • E-commerce (not natively, but includes Ecwid integration)
  • Client Billing
  • Code Export

Shopify offers full-featured e-commerce platform for more aadvanced stores.

  • Dashboard with a list of sites
  • Hosting
  • Code Export
  • Easy to use editor
  • CMS Editor for clients
  • Client Billing
  • Blog
  • E-commerce

Webflow offers full control over CSS using a visual interface.

  • Dashboard with a list of sites (not grouped)
  • Hosting
  • Code Export
  • Easy to use visual editor
  • CMS Editor for clients
  • Client Billing
  • Web Forms (drag and drop interface)
  • Blogs (supports multiple blogs)
  • E-commerce (coming soon)

Weebly Cloud is aimed at small, medium or large Web Design agencies. They offer:

  • Partner Portal
  • Hosting
  • White-Label
  • CMS with an easy to use visual editor
  • Web Forms (drag and drop interface with autoresponders)
  • Blogs (supports multiple blogs)
  • Secure Zones (Members & Groups)
  • Analytics
  • E-commerce
  • Email Accounts (via G Suite)
  • Email Marketing (coming soon via Weebly Promote Integration)
  • Domain Names (coming soon — manage and resell domain names)

WordPress is the most popular CMS platform and offers an almost unlimited variety of themes and plugins to be able to handue any website.

  • Any WordPress Hosting Company
  • Easy to use admin interface
  • CMS Editor for clients
  • Web Forms (drag and drop interface)
  • Blog
  • E-commerce via WooCommerce
  • Client Billing
  • Code Export
